# Auto-regenerated on every `news pull` / publish-live render. Tracking it
# in git would create cherry-pick conflicts every time it drifts (subscriber
# count, issue count) without adding any signal — pull.py rewrites it from
# scratch each run.
site/newsletter/_stats.yml
mlsysim/core/optimization/PLAN.md
book/quarto/contents/vol1/REVIEW_NOTES.md
book/quarto/contents/vol2/context_notes.md
book/tools/review_prompts.md
